1.2.0.name: wordpress/yt-eachuser
1.2.0.description:
The list of video is displayed specifying user of Youtube. The display form and the display sizes such as thumbnails and players can be selected.

shortcode [print_yt_EachUser] * ytname : youtube user name * type : player or thumbnail * width : width px (integer) * height : height px (integer) * num : view count (integer)

example: [print_yt_EachUser ytname="YouTube" type="player" width="425" height="355" num="3"]
